# Elevation + radius

Shadow scales, border-radius conventions, and depth language.

## Elevation / shadow scale

| Token | Use |
|---|---|
| `--elevation-0` | Flush / flat; no shadow |
| `--elevation-1` | Cards, list items |
| `--elevation-2` | Popovers, dropdowns |
| `--elevation-3` | Modals, sheets |
| `--elevation-4` | Toasts, tooltips |

Shadow values:
- `--shadow-sm`: {{e.g._0_1px_2px_rgba(0,0,0,0.05)}}
- `--shadow-md`: {{...}}
- `--shadow-lg`: {{...}}

## Radius scale

| Token | Value | Typical use |
|---|---|---|
| `--radius-none` | 0 | — |
| `--radius-sm` | {{4px}} | inputs, small buttons |
| `--radius-md` | {{8px}} | default buttons, cards |
| `--radius-lg` | {{12px}} | modals |
| `--radius-xl` | {{16px+}} | hero cards, pills |
| `--radius-full` | 9999 | avatars, pills |

## Rules

- Radius tokens only — no arbitrary `border-radius: 6px`
- Shadow tokens only — no arbitrary shadow values
- Elevation hierarchy matches visual stacking (modal above popover above card)
